Tools:
    1. angprofile.cpp > angprofile
        	measure the angular density of HEALPix Map fits file
    2. bulkvelprof.cpp > bulkvelprof
		measure the bulk velocity profile as well as the velocity distribution
    3. mapselect.cpp > mapselect
		select a region from a fits file (not finished)
    4. radialprofile.cpp > rprofile
       rprof_adi.cpp > rprof_adi (adiabatic contraction)
       rpf_shell.cpp > rpf_shell (shell method)
       rpf_shell_adi.cpp > rpf_shell_adi
		measure the radial profile    
    5. sampleparts.cpp
		sample particles from the tipsy file randomly
	